clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: For use in patients treated with Dabigatran when reversal of the anticoagulant effects of dabigatran is needed for emergency surgery urgent procedures and in life threatening or uncontrolled bleeding

contraindications.disease: In healthy volunteers the most frequently reported adverse reactions in greater than or equal to 5 of subjects treated with idarucizumab was headache In patients the most frequently reported adverse reactions in greater than or equal to 5 of patients treated with idarucizumab were hypokalemia delirium constipation pyrexia and pneumonia
